'''Holthion''' is a powerful [[demon]] found deep in the [[Underground Pass]]. Players must defeat him during the quest to obtain the amulet used as a key to a [[chest]] containing the [[Shadow of Iban]].

The other demons summoned by [[Kardia the Witch]] that hold amulets for the chest are [[Doomion]] and [[Othainian]].

